SubjectOrder Amending the Schedule to the First Nations Fiscal and Statistical Management Act
PrecisOrder Amending the SCHEDULE TO THE FIRST NATIONS FISCAL AND STATISTICAL MANAGEMENT ACT by adding four First Nations, in order to allow them to access some or all of the services provided by the fiscal institutions under the Act.
